Paper: hep-th/9310061

Date: 1993-10-12

Title: A Krichever--Novikov Formulation of W--Algebras on Riemann Surfaces

Comments: 13 pages. A remark about eq. $(1.8)$ has been added and a mistake in

eq. $(4.6)$ has been correctedJournal-ref: Phys.Lett. B323 (1994) 322-329

It is shown how the theory of classical $W$--algebras can be formulated on ahigher genus Riemann surface in the spirit of Krichever and Novikov. Anintriguing relation between the theory of $A_1$ embeddings into simple Liealgebras and the holomorphic geometry of Riemann surfaces is exihibited.